{"tid":1215700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"史上首次　台灣陸委會發佈「暫避免前往」香港警示","createTime":"2019-06-13T07:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:58:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"86baa96ee55a6578dd23954f2bcaad05e9e01af0","tid":1215700,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190612/_2019061218073896210.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190612%2F_2019061218073896210.jpeg&h=d2d08c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港政府執意修訂《逃犯條例》，先引發港人周日（9日）103萬人上街抗議，昨日（12日）更發起罷工、罷市、罷課，超過1萬名民眾包圍立法會大樓和政府總部等，遭警方武力驅趕。陸委會今日首次向香港發出「暫避免前往」的旅遊警示。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指出，香港數以萬計民眾參與昨日抗議《逃犯條例》示威活動，遭暴力驅趕爆發嚴重流血衝突，導致逾70位市民受傷。香港立法會、港府總部周邊地區仍有群眾聚集，部份地鐵站交通運輸受到影響，後續示威活動將有可能再次發生。陸委會提醒近期計劃前往香港的台灣民眾，注意個人安全，勿前往相關地點，並隨時留意交通資訊及事態發展，以免影響行程及安全。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指出，香港發生民眾抗議示威活動，爆發嚴重流血衝突，提醒台灣民眾要注意旅遊安全，或暫時避免前往。如果台灣民眾在香港旅遊，或台商、台灣鄉親在港遭遇問題，可即時致電香港辦事處急難救助電話（61439012），辦事處將提供相關協助。<br />\n<br />\n翻查陸委會官網的「陸港澳旅遊警示專區」，以往發出的旅遊警示都針對大陸的天災及疫情，唯一一次與香港有關的，是2009年香港確診首例H1N1禽流感後，陸委會當時稱香港疫情相當於「黃燈旅遊警示」，但沒發警示，僅呼籲前往香港的台灣民眾，要注意防護措施。"},{"pid":"5d7b00ff142761343701118a4e3a7e1ff898bbc0","tid":1215700,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764a1e0acd5607e94dc4110454cf4c082946ffa4","tid":1215700,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190613/59711087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711087&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=95d53ed5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59711087&h=8041b204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190613/59711087</a>"},{"pid":"87717ddf7c4b69e7c84799d93a1eece49409a8f6","tid":1215700,"uid":196924,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"港獨之父 梁振英<br />\n焦土之母 林鄭月娥"},{"pid":"d0e36ef9eea106160fd80f7744dade70a33f0fd9","tid":1215700,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6034e4e017d7037f8a290c0716ef80b334895d","tid":1215700,"uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"87717ddf7c4b69e7c84799d93a1eece49409a8f6","tid":1215700,"uid":196924,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"港獨之父 梁振英<br />\n焦土之母 林鄭月娥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"支爆大帝 習近平"},{"pid":"8a8dd212749112e332ca9acef807bb9af8ae17e3","tid":1215700,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"我哋都應該避免前往高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[旅遊台置頂] 有韓國瑜條奶共撚樣做市長一日，我哋香港人請罷去高雄！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1214842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1214842</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4bc1024c04854c8896ae2b50dd47517fd73379ae","tid":1215700,"uid":5822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好去高雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣人唔好黎香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好全部國家向香港發旅遊警示 等班仆街驚"},{"pid":"4cb7c0d4d83c09cd6794a075c567055812a98871","tid":1215700,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bc1024c04854c8896ae2b50dd47517fd73379ae","tid":1215700,"uid":5822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"